OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F399A1735475965
OL,3,CStudent hopes to become first ever
OL,4,CDeafblind person to climb Mount Everest
OL,6,F"Around 18, 19 I started to become
OL,7,Fvery clumsy, very clumsy, and they
OL,8,Fnoticed I have no peripheral sight.
OL,10,F"And that's when I got referred to a
OL,11,Fspecialist and we found I have Usher
OL,12,Fsyndrome."
OL,14,FShe has now set herself a series of
OL,15,Ftasks and milestones to complete
OL,16,Fbefore taking on the challenge of
OL,17,Fclimbing Everest in 2026.
OL,19,F"I'm treating each milestone as a way
OL,20,Fto check if I really want to
OL,21,Fcontinue," she added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
