OL,3,CStudent hopes to become first ever
OL,4,CDeafblind person to climb Mount Everest
OL,6,FShe says it makes her more determined
OL,7,Fthan ever to complete her goal.
OL,9,F"I don't know how to express it," she
OL,10,Fsaid. "I think a lot of people can see
OL,11,Fit. It will happen."
